{"tid":2135758,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"（Netflix 講五眼聯盟）松樹谷的竊聽人生Pine Gap","createTime":"2020-08-01T16:18:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T08:50:06.000Z","uid":240448,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3f67926d34386010d16264af4965484eca061c7e","tid":2135758,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T16:18:39.000Z","msg":"在美澳最高機密的聯合防禦設施「松樹谷」中，間諜彼此合作又互相算計，使得這個重要的結盟漸漸出現裂痕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TcXnkyF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTcXnkyF.png&h=079d9e7f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4EymA62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4EymA62.jpg&h=8e7ebc53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><em><strong>[black]<span class=\"limegreen\">//如果你是政治咖，Netflix 的 Pine Gap 超好看！推！<br />\n<br />\nPine Gap 劇集以一個位於澳洲，但由美澳合作的，以監聽為主要任務的軍事基地做為背景，裡面的不管是美籍澳藉人物都在做史諾登以前幫美國國家安全局做的事。在這次<span class=\"red\">華為</span>事件裡，提到的「五眼」，就是講美澳這樣合作交換情報的操作。 // </span>[/black]</strong></em></span> <br />\n<br />\n影評：范琪斐的時間<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<em><span class=\"blue\">Pine Gap 基地在做什麼呢？<br />\n<br />\n據 Nautilus Institute 網站內容，Pine Gap 基地有三大監聽任務：<br />\n<br />\n1. 自冷戰起，該基地負責控制和指揮在地球同步軌道內的監察衞星，以上衞星都是由美國中情局所有，用作全球監視之用途。Pine Gap內有38具大型天線，當中大部份都是用來聯繫同步衞星。<br />\n<br />\n2. 監察洲際飛彈發射，提供早期預報資料予美國和其盟友，及攔截對敵對勢力之發彈。Pine Gap 主要監視地區包括中東、西太平洋地區。<br />\n<br />\n3. 為五眼聯盟提供情報和監聽。數年前爆料的美國前NSA 僱員也提過Pine Gap 基地曾監聽全澳洲國內上網、電話等通訊。<br />\n<br />\n喜歡陰謀論、又或者喜歡看諜戰、情報戰的朋友，不妨一看。即使劇集在2018年推出，即使在2020看，也不會覺得過時和脫離現實。劇內出現的恐怖組織、南海紛爭、國際之間不信任，也是真真實實出現在我們生活之中。我們生在香港，無論回歸前後，都是東、西兩大陣營的重要情報戰場。疫情之下，我們又會何去何從呢？<br />\n</span></em><br />\n<a href=\"https://blog.wingleung.me/2020/04/%E5%B1%85%E5%AE%B6%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB%E7%9D%87-netflix-pine-gap-%E6%9D%BE%E6%A8%B9%E8%B0%B7.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.wingleung.me%2F2020%2F04%2F%25E5%25B1%2585%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2596%25AB%25E7%259D%2587-netflix-pine-gap-%25E6%259D%25BE%25E6%25A8%25B9%25E8%25B0%25B7.html&d=e0fscszCypj9zTmdFU62PnjL6x1fkqqvETpDxuWVMK8%3D&h=1440a1df\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.wingleung.me/2020/04/%E5%B1%85%E5%AE%B6%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB%E7%9D%87-netflix-pine-gap-%E6%9D%BE%E6%A8%B9%E8%B0%B7.html</a>"},{"pid":"91f5bceee8f035e2e9e9226a5e922fb33de31b85","tid":2135758,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T16:20:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zWvZEYVa9A0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzWvZEYVa9A0&d=e0fscszCypj9zTmdFU62PnjL6x1fkqqvETpDxuWVMK8%3D&h=989266e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zWvZEYVa9A0</a>"},{"pid":"2a96d5bb8db63319d28a626523e3a636ca5852c6","tid":2135758,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T16:26:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無人睇左"},{"pid":"2f65d416fb7f09c7cdc5f61866858beac2412cd4","tid":2135758,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T16:42:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22a4d2dc426433b646da93e0593ef360a580bda1","tid":2135758,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a96d5bb8db63319d28a626523e3a636ca5852c6","tid":2135758,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T16:26:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無人睇左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T16:52:27.000Z","msg":"上年睇曬，故事 ok"},{"pid":"4dc1c1c10a3779737680ff53271067a720ca090e","tid":2135758,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T16:52:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\"